&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;ES-MX&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Founded in 1985, ATS is a company with a presence in the United States, Mexico and the United Kingdom. We are professionals in Industrial Maintenance and we make factories run better.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;ES-MX&quot;&gt;Fundada en 1985, ATS es una empresa con presencia en los Estados Unidos, México y el Reino Unido. Somos profesionales en mantenimiento industrial y hacemos que las fábricas funcionen mejor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today we have an opening as a Business Intelligence Analyst , if you meet the requirements please apply through the website including your resume.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborates with business functions to collects business intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translates non-technical requirements into technical business requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifies process inefficiencies and recommends alternative solutions and process improvements through evaluating user impacts, cost benefit analysis, processing specifications, and technology trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifies, defines, and documents analytical requirements for new metrics and reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designs, develops, and maintains business solutions based on business requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilizes data collection techniques, including interviews, document analysis, workshops, surveys, business process descriptions, use cases, scenarios, business analysis, and task and workflow analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interprets data utilizing a variety of techniques, ranging from simple data aggregation via statistical analysis to complex data mining.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitors reports and solutions, ensures data and reporting accuracy, and reconciles conflicts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversees project tasks and cross-training through mentoring team members on software / tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to learn new applications, processes, and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical, statistical, quantitative, and deduction skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with data warehouse deployments and writing software requirements and test specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize and oversee multiple projects in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced knowledge of MS Office, SQL Server, Power BI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to build relationships and work well across functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Three to five years of project management experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Firm understanding of business processes, finance, management, and accounting principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Please call or send your resume to 811 611 6900&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
