&lt;p&gt;Performs expert level electronic component level repairs, using complex techniques and procedures to analyze, troubleshoot and repair complex problems on a specialized product or piece of equipment (for example, Drives (AC, DC, VFD, Servo) PLC’s, Power Supplies ,HMI’s, Laser scanners, AC Motors, DC Motors, Servo Motors, Circuit Boards, and other Industrial electronics). Requires advanced level of electronic component level expertise and aptitude. Works under minimal supervision and requires extensive knowledge and experience in a specialized discipline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Principal Duties/Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Repairs and troubleshoots electronics of advanced complexity at the component level.&lt;/p&gt;
